text: I woke up with tremendous pain,
the serum had come out from my arm.
Me with a tremendous pain,
and then they took us out and told us that we had to go home.
As for me I had been 3 months pregnant,
I suffered with my little child there
until 7 months.
I wasn’t well anymore,
the belly was very swollen
and the doctor who was checking me told me
it was better if I travelled to Piura
because here they wouldn’t be able to…
I went to say goodbye to my children,
I had 7 small children.
They took me to my village of Rodeo Pampa
to say goodbye and go to Piura.
And then around 1 am
I woke up with a tremendous pain and
I stood up
and I dropped big gush of blood,
like a hemorrhage.
And...
around 6, 7 am.
I don’t remember much,
but the midwife had already made me give birth.
Well, my child he died,
I have been bad
and still am bad until now.
